cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with disaster analysis using images shared on social media outlets. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper deals with data collection and analysis, which could place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
